{
  "stem": "3022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I remember very distinctly, we used to bend parts for the [NON-ENGLISH], 50 transport planes, because they had corrugated bodies and they were shot up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We had to make, you know, we had to make replacement parts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The, the, the factory functioned six days a week, day and night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The shifts were 12-hour shifts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The-- the one shift was manned by the Jewish workers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "One shift was manned by the Polish worker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You, you were given blueprints and a work order.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And if you were not skillful and by, by accident, you ruined the work or so on, your number was taken down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And at an appropriate time, several days later, when there was enough people whose number was taken down, you were taken out and shot.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Similarly, the killing grounds were outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They were called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "These were the killing grounds were they were bringing in Jewish people who were turned in by the Poles, from the foreigners.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They were brought in and they were executed, mostly by the gestapo from the town of Mielec.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "The price, supposedly, for a Jewish head, was a pack of cigarettes or a pound of sugar.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And it must have been a scarce commodity, because there were many Jews who were being shot over there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We knew when and how they were shot, because people from the camp had to go and dig their graves and bring their clothing [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they told us how they were shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They were undressed, made down to kneel over the grave, and shot in the back of the head.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And the reason we knew that was true, because the clothes that they brought, they were not stained with blood.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "They were clean.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
